  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>For those looking for 5 star levels of comfort and service, Le Meridien Fairway offers excellent value for money.  The local department of tourism classifies it  as a four star since it does not have a 3 restaurants and a 24 hour laundry service. (TM07.08)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>Located in Deira, overlooking the Dubai Creek Gold Club and 5 minutes drive from Deira City Centre Shopping Mall and Dubai Airport. The hotel has easy accessibility for Sheikh Zayed Road and is approximately 15 kms from Jumeirah.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Each of the rooms are large in size and decorated in different colours of blue, red, purple etc depending on the floor.  Every room is appointed to a very high standard and although the hotel is officially classified as a four star the rooms are superior to many five star hotel rooms in the city.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The building has a modern glass facade.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel has ornate Indian restaurant where breakfast is served and a large coffee shop on the ground floor.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The lobby has a two story atrium with a large marble staircase in the middle and the coffee shop on the left hand side where there is also a small seating area.</Text>
  </Description>
